    "steps": [
      "Wash the rice in several changes of water until clear. Soak for 30 minutes, then drain.",
      "In a pot over medium heat, dry roast the lentils for 2-3 minutes until golden and nutty. Wash them thoroughly.",
      "Combine the rice, lentils, and 3½ cups of water in a pot. Add ginger, turmeric, and 2 tablespoons of ghee. Bring to a boil, skim off foam, then cook over low heat for 20 minutes.",
      "Add another ½ cup of water and cook for 5 more minutes until creamy. Mash slightly to achieve a risotto-like texture.",
      "Meanwhile, fry cashews in ghee until golden and set aside.",
      "In the same pan, add cumin, pepper, and asafoetida to the remaining ghee, frying until fragrant. Pour this over the rice mixture.",
      "Mix in coconut, salt, and the fried cashews, reserving some for garnish. Serve hot.",
      "Serve, smile, and enjoy your homemade feast!"
